These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-1::.
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, amaryllis, marigold, rose, daffodil, zinnia, begonia
There are 7 different nationalities: argentine, australian, canadian, chinese, mexican, nigerian, thai
 1. the person who growsrose is on the left of the chinese##1
 2. the mexican is the person who growsrose##1
 3. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
 4. the canadian is on the right of the nigerian##1
 5. the person who growsmarigold is in the middle##1
 6. the argentine is on the far left##1
 7. the person who growsdaffodil is the argentine##1
 8. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the right of the nigerian##1
 9. the canadian is on the left of the australian##1
10. the chinese is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1
11. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the australian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3       |    4     |      5      |       6       |      7       |
| Flower           | daffodil | rose | amaryllis | marigold | balloon-flower | zinnia | begonia |
| Nationality   | argentine    | mexican   | chinese      | nigerian | canadian    | australian    | thai         |

