.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-3::.
There 7 different types of food: corn, cucumber, lemon, lettuce, onion, pepper, spinach
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: electronic, ambient, house, folk, metal, trance, jazz
 1. the person eating cucumber is on the left of the person eating onion##1
 2. the person eating onion is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
 3. the fan of ambient is on the left of the person eating spinach##1
 4. the person eating corn is on the right of the person eating pepper##1
 5. the fan of electronic is the person eating onion##1
 6. the fan of house is on the right of the fan of ambient##1
 7. the fan of ambient is on the left of the fan of house##1
 8. the fan of ambient is on the right of the fan of folk##1
 9. the person eating pepper is the fan of folk##1
10. the person eating lemon is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
11. the fan of folk is in the middle##1
12. the person eating spinach is on the left of the fan of metal##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |   3    |      4       |     5      |    6     |     7     |
| Food   | cucumber | onion     | lemon  | pepper       | corn       | spinach  | lettuce   |
| Music-Genre    | trance  | electronic | jazz | folk | ambient | house | metal |

