.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-4::.
City: liverpool, berlin, prague, nizza, rome, hamburg, miami
There are 7 different nationalities: argentine, australian, egyptian, indian, indonesian, nigerian, thai
 1. the person traveling to rome is the australian##1
 2. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
 3. the nigerian is on the right of the egyptian##1
 4. the argentine is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
 5. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
 6. the person traveling to hamburg is on the far left##1
 7. the egyptian is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
 8. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the nigerian##1
 9. the person traveling to prague is the indonesian##1
10. the indonesian is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1
11. the thai is the person traveling to berlin##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |  5   |     6      |     7     |
| City   | hamburg    | miami     | nizza     | prague      | berlin | rome      | liverpool     |
| Nationality   | indian | egyptian | nigerian | indonesian | thai | australian | argentine |

