.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-5::.
City: colone, paris, prague, berlin, rome, marseilles, san-francisco
7 different pets are kept: dog, fish, frog, goldfish, guinea-pig, horse, snake
 1. the person traveling to paris is the owner of the snake##1
 2. the owner of the fish is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
 3. the owner of the horse is in the middle##1
 4. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
 5. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person traveling to marseilles##1
 6. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
 7. the owner of the horse is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 8. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1
 9. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
10. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |      5      |      6       |      7      |
| City   | paris | prague | marseilles     | berlin | san-francisco | rome | colone |
| Pet     | snake   | frog    | guinea-pig | horse     | dog         | goldfish     | fish        |

