The people have 7 different hobbies: writing, filmmaking, puzzles, camping, collecting, dancing, rock-climbing
 1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
 2. the person drinking 7up is the person who's hobby is writing##1
 3. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 4. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 5. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
 6. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
 7. the person drinking iced-tea is in the middle##1
 8. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 9. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
10. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |  3  |    4     |    5    |   6   |      7      |
| Beverage    | coffee | soy-milk   | 7up | iced-tea | sprite  | juice | almond-milk |
| Hobby   | camping   | collecting | writing | dancing     | filmmaking | rock-climbing | puzzles   |

