.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-7::.
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: november, september, january, august, april, july, june
The people use 7 different means of transport: boat, jet-ski, motorbike, roller, skateboard, snowmobile, trike
 1. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in june is the person driving the roller##1
 4. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
 6. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
 7. the person driving the boat is the person who's birthday is in january##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in april is in the middle##1
 9. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
10. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3   |      4       |     5      |     6     |   7   |
| Birthday   | november  | june | august | april | july     | september | january |
| Transport     | snowmobile | roller      | trike | motorbike    | skateboard | jet-ski   | boat  |

