 4. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the pall-mall-smoker##1
 5. the dannemann-smoker is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
 6. the cain-smoker is the person watching family movies##1
 7. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
 8. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the old-henry-smoker##1
 9. the person watching martial-arts movies is in the middle##1
10. the dannemann-smoker is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3     |      4       |  5   |     6     |     7      |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | family | western   | martial-arts | epic | adventure | spy        |
| Cigar     | baccarat | cain | pall-mall | oliveros         | old-henry  | dannemann    | montecristo |

